 <H1>Modifying Records</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>UPDATE command used to modify fields of existing tuples.
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>WHERE clause is applied first and determines fields to be modified.  SET clause determines new values.
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>If field being modified is also used to determine new value, value on rhs is old value.</H2>
</UL></P>
<P><UL>
UPDATE  Sailors S
<BR></UL><UL>
SET  S.rating=S.rating-1
</UL><UL>
WHERE  S.age &#060 15</UL></P>
